  "text": "Remark 3.13. One can extend construction of integrals from Remark 3.11 to generalised Calogero-Moser type systems which do not have full Coxeter symmetry and which correspond to special representations of rational Cherednik algebras in quotients of the polynomial representation [CITATION_1] (see also [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] ). Indeed, invariant combinations of operators A i at γ = 0 in a suitable gauge act in such a quotient and hence lead to additional quantum integrals for the corresponding Hamiltonian.",
